# Mutation Swarm 2D

Lee `AGENTS.md` para stack, convenciones y skills.

- Motor: Unity 6000.3.x, C#, 2D
- Namespaces: `MutationSwarm.Core`, `.Entities`, `.Combat`, `.Evolution`, `.Building`, `.UI`
- Eventos globales: `Script_03_EventBus` — no acoplar UI a gameplay con singletons ad hoc
- Build: `build.ps1` o `Tools → Mutation Swarm → Build Windows`
- Diseño: `design/` (GDDs). Etapa actual: `production/stage.txt`
